Package org.howard.edu.lsp.assignment6

Class IntegerSet

java.lang.Object
org.howard.edu.lsp.assignment6.IntegerSet
public class IntegerSet extends Object
Models a mathematical set of integers backed by an ArrayList.

Invariants:

  • No duplicate integers are stored.
  • All mutator operations modify this instance (no new objects returned).

This class supports standard set operations such as union, intersection, difference, and complement. It disallows duplicates and throws an exception when operations requiring elements (like largest() or smallest()) are invoked on an empty set.
